<div class="entry-content"><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="1000" height="1500" src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Creamy-Parmesan-Chicken-and-Butternut-Squash-Skillet-NEW.png"   data-pin-description="This Creamy Parmesan Chicken and Butternut Squash Skillet Recipe is an easy, luscious and hearty one skillet dinnertime favorite. This yummy chicken dinner combines a flavorful parmesan cream sauce packed with garlic, spinach, fresh thyme and roasted butternut squash and chicken thighs. This one skillet meal will become a go-to dinner recipe for the fall and winter. #AFullLiving #ChickenButternutSquash #EasyChickenDinner #HealthyChickenDinner #CreamyChickenSkillet #OneSkilletDinner"  alt="graphic with text of Creamy Parmesan Chicken and Butternut Squash Skillet Recipe" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner"  /></div><span id="dpsp-post-content-markup" data-image-pin-it="true"></span>
<p>This Creamy Parmesan Chicken and Butternut Squash Skillet Recipe is an easy, luscious, and hearty one-skillet dinnertime favorite. This yummy butternut s<meta charset="utf-8">quash chicken dinner combines a flavorful parmesan cream sauce packed with garlic, spinach, fresh thyme, and roasted butternut squash and chicken thighs. This one-skillet meal will become a go-to dinner recipe for the fall and winter.  </p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1799" fetchpriority="high" src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13.jpg" alt="Chicken thighs sitting in butternut and garlic parmesan sauce" data-skip-lazy class="wp-image-32760" style="object-fit:cover" srcset="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13.jpg 1200w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13-400x600.jpg 400w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-13.jpg"></figure>    <div class="dpsp-email-save-this-tool " style="background-color: #f4e4e1;">        <div class="hubbub-save-this-form-wrapper"><h3 class="hubbub-save-this-heading">Save This Recipe! &#128140;</h3><div class="hubbub-save-this-message"><p>We'll email this post to you, so you can come back to it later!</p></div><div class="hubbub-save-this-form-only-wrapper"><form name="hubbub-save-this-form" method="post" action="">                    <input type="text" name="hubbub-save-this-snare" class="hubbub-save-this-snare hubbub-block-save-this-snare"><p class="hubbub-save-this-name-paragraph-wrapper"><input aria-label="First Name" type="text" placeholder="First Name" name="hubbub-save-this-name" value="" class="hubbub-block-save-this-text-control hubbub-save-this-name" required></p><p class="hubbub-save-this-emailaddress-paragraph-wrapper"><input aria-label="Email Address" type="email" placeholder="Email Address" name="hubbub-save-this-emailaddress" value="" class="hubbub-block-save-this-text-control hubbub-save-this-emailaddress" required></p><p class="hubbub-save-this-consent-paragraph-wrapper"><input type="checkbox" name="hubbub-save-this-consent" class="hubbub-save-this-consent" value="1" required> <label for="hubbub-save-this-consent">I agree to be sent email.</label></p><p class="hubbub-save-this-submit-button-paragraph-wrapper"><input type="submit" style="background-color:#2d4654;color:#ffffff;" value="Save This Recipe" class="hubbub-block-save-this-submit-button" name="hubbub-block-save-this-submit-button"></p><input type="hidden" name="hubbub-save-this-postid" class="hubbub-save-this-postid" value="16517">                    <input type="hidden" name="hubbub-save-this-posturl" class="hubbub-save-this-posturl" value="https://afullliving.com/chicken-butternut-squash-recipe/">                    <input type="hidden" name="hubbub-save-this-posttitle" class="hubbub-save-this-posttitle" value="Chicken and Butternut Squash Recipe with Parmesan Sauce"></form>            </div></div>    </div></div>


<p><strong>Disclosure</strong>: This post is a paid partnership with our wonderful friends at <a href="https://www.lodgecastiron.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow external" data-wpel-link="external">Lodge Cast Iron</a>! As you know, we have been huge fans of their amazing cookware for years, and we use it in the majority of our recipes. </p>



<p>We utilized their Blacklock 12 inch skillet to make this hearty and delicious feast. Blacklock cookware comes triple seasoned, so that it's naturally non-stick. It's quite lightweight as well! This versatile skillet is now our go-to for dinners, desserts, roasted veggies, and more. Thank you for supporting brands that help us in making awesome content! </p>



<p><strong><em>Now, onto the recipe!</em></strong></p>



<p>This dinner recipe is simply irresistible. Chicken thighs drenched in a creamy, garlicky parmesan sauce with spinach, butternut squash, and fresh thyme.  What's not to love? </p>



<p><meta charset="utf-8">This dinner is buttery, hearty, creamy, cheesy, herbaceous, savory, and just a tad bit sweet from the butternut squash. It's so easy to make all in one skillet. No mess and the whole family will enjoy this. What a way to enjoy cooler weather produce and extra veggies! </p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Chicken and butternut squash skillet with parmesan sauce" class="wp-image-32757" style="object-fit:cover" data-lazy-srcset="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10.jpg 1200w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-400x600.jpg 400w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-150x225.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1799" src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10.jpg" alt="Chicken and butternut squash skillet with parmesan sauce" class="wp-image-32757" style="object-fit:cover" srcset="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10.jpg 1200w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-400x600.jpg 400w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-10.jpg"></noscript></figure></div>


<p>If you're looking for more tasty chicken dinners, be sure to check out this <a href="https://afullliving.com/baked-chicken-feta-sheet-pan-dinner/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">baked feta chicken sheet pan dinner</a>, this <a href="https://afullliving.com/chicken-wrapped-parma-ham/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">chicken wrapped in parma ham stuffed with mozzarella</a>, or this <a href="https://afullliving.com/jalapeno-popper-chicken-skillet/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">jalape&ntilde;o popper chicken skillet</a>. </p>



<p>You may also enjoy this <a href="https://afullliving.com/pumpkin-pasta-sauce/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">pumpkin pasta sauce</a>, this <a href="https://afullliving.com/keto-butternut-squash-soup/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">keto butternut squash soup</a>, or this <a href="https://afullliving.com/keto-candied-butternut-squash/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">roasted butternut squash with brown sugar</a>. </p>


