data-pin-media="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-2.jpg"></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1799" data-id="32763" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="butternut squash and spinach cooking in bone broth" class="wp-image-32763" data-lazy-srcset="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3.jpg 1200w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-150x225.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3.jpg"><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1799" data-id="32763" src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3.jpg" alt="butternut squash and spinach cooking in bone broth" class="wp-image-32763" srcset="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3.jpg 1200w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-pin-media="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-new-3.jpg"></noscript></figure>
</figure>



<p>Stir in the heavy whipping cream and parmesan cheese to the skillet and cook until cheese is mostly melted, then nestle in the chicken thighs, skin side up.</p>



