<h2 id="chicken-and-butternut-squash-recipe-with-parmesan-sauce"   class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Chicken and Butternut Squash Recipe with Parmesan Sauce</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<span class="wprm-recipe-details wprm-recipe-author wprm-block-text-light"><a href="https://afullliving.com/about" target="_self" data-wpel-link="internal" rel="noopener noreferrer">Briana</a></span>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">This Creamy Parmesan Chicken and Butternut Squash Skillet Recipe is an easy, luscious and hearty one skillet dinner time favorite. This yummy butternut squash  chicken dinner combines a flavorful parmesan cream sauce packed with garlic, spinach, fresh thyme and roasted butternut squash and chicken thighs. This one skillet meal will become a go-to dinner recipe for the fall and winter. </span></div>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
