		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
Perfect flavor in this dish! I used boneless, skinless thighs because I had them on hand. Otherwise, I followed the recipe. Thank you for a simple to make and delicious dish.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-47720" data-commentid="47720" data-postid="16517" data-belowelement="article-comment-47720" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Debra" aria-label="Reply to Debra">Reply</a></div>
		
