	<article id="article-comment-47721">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Briana</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">October 28, 2025 at 7:13 pm</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Totally makes sense Debra, and thighs can stand up to a long cooking time regardless! We're so thrilled you loved the recipe! Thank you so much for your feedback! 🙂</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-47721" data-commentid="47721" data-postid="16517" data-belowelement="article-comment-47721" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Briana" aria-label="Reply to Briana">Reply</a></div>
		
