	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-10889">
	<article id="article-comment-10889">

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Tori</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">September 29, 2023 at 6:13 pm</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Holy pepper, Batman!<br />
Is there a typo?  I made it with the 2 TABLESPOONs per the recipe and 😵‍💫</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-10889" data-commentid="10889" data-postid="16517" data-belowelement="article-comment-10889" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Tori" aria-label="Reply to Tori">Reply</a></div>
		
	</article>
	<ul class="children">

