		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<span class="comment-author-name">Briana</span> <span class="says">says</span>			</p>

			<p class="comment-meta"><time class="comment-time">September 29, 2023 at 9:13 pm</time></p>		</header>

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Tori, we're so sorry, this was absolutely a typo! 😅 We'd suggest about a 1/2 a TEASPOON to start.. no idea how that amount got in there. Thank you for bringing this attention!</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-10890" data-commentid="10890" data-postid="16517" data-belowelement="article-comment-10890" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Briana" aria-label="Reply to Briana">Reply</a></div>
		
