			<p><img class="wprm-comment-rating" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://afullliving.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-recipe-maker/assets/icons/rating/stars-alt-5.svg" alt="5 stars" width="80" height="16" /><br />
Wow!!  SOOO yummy - every bite just melted!   Will definitely be putting this into the rotation!  Only change I made was to use 1.5 lbs of boneless chicken tenders (because that's what I had in the fridge tonight...)  I've already sent this link to about 4 different family members to try!  I NEVER leave comments - but this was so delicious, I needed to shout it out!</p>
